      <title>朝鲜在韩国岛附近发射炮弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/north-korea-fires-artillery-near-s-korean-island-yonhap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在朝鲜领导人金正恩表示不可能与邻国统一后，朝鲜向朝鲜半岛西海岸的一个韩国边境岛屿发射了约 200 枚炮弹，给首尔带来了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/north-korea-fires-artillery-near-s-korean-island-yonhap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:53:16 GMT</pubDate>
