    <item>
      <title>中国称缅甸去年移交了 41,000 名诈骗嫌疑人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-says-myanmar-handed-over-41-000-scam-suspects-last-year-lr05s315</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，缅甸将 41,000 名涉及电信诈骗的嫌疑人移交给中国，北京方面继续打击这一非法行业，该行业已从毫无戒心的受害者手中窃取了数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-says-myanmar-handed-over-41-000-scam-suspects-last-year-lr05s315</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:51:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯和黑莉试图通过攻击特朗普来影响共和党选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/desantis-tries-to-sway-republican-voters-with-attacks-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离爱荷华州举行 2024 年首场共和党总统竞选还有不到两周时间，罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 和妮基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 在爱荷华州市政厅通过电视转播攻击共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/desantis-tries-to-sway-republican-voters-with-attacks-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 03:50:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于反对派抵制选举，美国向孟加拉国施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/upcoming-bangladesh-election-puts-democracy-and-us-ties-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜将在周日举行的遭到抵制的选举中延长其 15 年的统治。现在的问题是，以美国为首的西方政府是否会惩罚美国的民主倒退，并拉近其与中国的距离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/upcoming-bangladesh-election-puts-democracy-and-us-ties-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚致命爆炸使电池金属野心在总统投票前成为人们关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/explosion-in-indonesia-puts-china-backed-nickel-expansion-in-focus-ahead-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚一家中资工厂发生的致命爆炸凸显了雅加达雄心勃勃地押注电池金属加工以加速工业发展的隐性成本，这是即将卸任领导人佐科·维多多(Joko Widodo)的一项标志性政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/explosion-in-indonesia-puts-china-backed-nickel-expansion-in-focus-ahead-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:43:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本紧急寻找地震后失踪的222人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/japan-rushes-to-find-240-people-missing-after-earthquake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本在新年当天的西北半岛地震中紧急寻找 222 名失踪人员，当局称寻找被困在废墟下的幸存者的时间已经不多了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/japan-rushes-to-find-240-people-missing-after-earthquake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:25:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红海袭击和伊朗爆炸后布林肯前往中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿安东尼·布林肯启程前往中东，这是自 10 月 7 日以色列遇袭以来第四次访问中东，这是美国应对更广泛地区冲突日益增长的风险的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南在滥用权力调查中拘留越南石油公司前主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/vietnam-detains-ex-petrovietnam-chair-in-power-abuse-probe-lqz4kcna</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南警方拘留了越南石油天然气集团（也称为 PetroVietnam）的前董事长，他也是前贸易副部长，因为政府监察办公室批评该部门缺乏监督，未能发现石油贸易商的违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/vietnam-detains-ex-petrovietnam-chair-in-power-abuse-probe-lqz4kcna</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 11:29:30 GMT</pubDate>
